description: This is a 1st of a new series where I go visit my popular models at their homes. I thought it would be cool to see them in their real environment. My first visit is at Brad's. He suggested that I shoot his full body workout in his living room. I asked him, full body workout? He answered yes, every single muscle involved! Yummy! Hope you'll enjoy this new Maskurbate reality series!
title: At Home With Brad, Scene #01
